ishable from conventional science apart from the participation of volunteers. When properly designed, carried out, and evaluated, citizen science can provide sound science, efficiently generate high-quality data, and help solve problems.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "McKinley, Duncan C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Miller-Rushing, Abe J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ballard, Heidi L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bonney, Rick", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Brown, Hutch", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Cook-Patton, Susan C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Evans, Daniel M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "French, Rebecca A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Parrish, Julia K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Phillips, Tina B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ryan, Sean F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Shanley, Lea A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Shirk, Jennifer L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Stepenuck, Kristine F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Weltzin, Jake F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wiggins, Andrea", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Boyle, Owen D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Briggs, Russell D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chapin, Stuart F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hewitt, David A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Preuss, Peter W.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Soukup, Michael A.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 2", "Chapter 6", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/9758bef80c15e9ec19087b2ea349c6a2", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/b3953b576493e30e38f94f6ac398d98008ce808f5661748abbf59ce990c8225e", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/NRZ5ZHP4", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2